org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.plan

Class VectorReduceSinkInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.plan.VectorReduceSinkInfo

  • public class VectorReduceSinkInfo
extends Object
    VectorGroupByAggregrationInfo. A convenience data structure that has information needed to vectorize reduce sink. It is created by the Vectorizer when it is determining whether it can specialize so the information doesn't have to be recreated again and agains by the VectorReduceSinkOperator's constructors and later during execution.
